  Q. Are you both feeling a bit of momentum turning towards the Europeans?  
 GRAEME McDOWELL: I think that's the way this Ryder Cup goes. It's momentum for the Reds and it keeps going. I think the pendulum is going to be swung a little bit in either direction so we are going to be going out with all guns blazing this afternoon.   
   
